---
import PageLayout from '../../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';

export const prerender = true;

const lang = 'en';
const title = 'Round Tables';
const pageTitle = 'Round Tables on Civil Society Development';
---

<PageLayout title={title} lang={lang} pageTitle={pageTitle}>
  <p><strong>Date:</strong> 2024</p>
  <p>The Public Association «Counterpart-Sheriktesh» held a series of round tables on topical issues of civil society development in Kyrgyzstan.</p>
  <p>The round tables were devoted to the following topics:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Civil society participation in state decision-making</li>
    <li>Transparency and accountability of state bodies</li>
    <li>Public oversight mechanisms</li>
    <li>Development of volunteering and charity</li>
  </ul>
  <p>The events were attended by representatives of NGOs, state bodies, international organizations and active citizens.</p>
</PageLayout>
